   <S PAR='1' RSNT='1' SNO='1'>CONTENTS The Remembrance of the Lord 1 The Remembrance of the Lord 2 The Worship of the Father Practical Fellowship concerning the Lord's Table Meeting Further Significances of the Lord's Table Meeting Discerning the Body Supplemental Reading PREFACE</S>
   <S PAR='2' RSNT='1' SNO='2'>The contents of the outlines in this book are from notes and printed publications of Brother Witness Lee that have been released by him from 1964 through 1990.</S>
   <S PAR='3' RSNT='1' SNO='3'>Our brother points out that the Lord's table meeting is the most important meeting of a local church.</S>
   <S PAR='4' RSNT='1' SNO='4'>We pray that these outlines will uplift our vision and practice of the Lord's table meeting as we remember Him and display His death until He comes 1 Cor 11:26 .</S>
